latestIgtvVideos.title: Quick everyday makeup
How to achieve the bold lips and neutral eyes look
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Products used for this look:
Eyes :
Concealer on the lids 1.)@lagirlcosmetics pro conceal concealer in shade medium beige(that’s my shade)
2.)Set that with the @lauramercier translucent powder.
3.)Eye pencil was by @shiseido the microtip eyeliner ink
4.)@nyxcosmetics @nyxcosmetics_in ultimate edit eye shadow palette.
5.)@shuuemura eyelash curler 
6.)@maccosmeticsindia @maccosmetics 3D mascara 
7.)@benefitcosmetics @benefitindia brow zing palette  in no.3 for my eyebrows and a clear brow gel by @kryolanuk for setting them in place.

Face:
1.) Under eyes I used my @lagirlcosmetics pro conceal concealer in the shade medium beige and to brighten I used @maybelline instant age rewind  eraser in the shade medium (these are suitable for my under eyes)
2.) set this and my the shiny parts of my face with @lauramercier translucent powder.
3.) contoured with @benefitindia hoola powder
4.) To add some color on the cheeks used a bronzer from @kikomilano @kikomilanoindia bake bronzer in no.2
5.) Cream highlighter used my @narsissist nars orgasm palette and went over it with my @kajabeauty highlighter powder.

Lips:
1.) To lone the lips I used my Kiko lip pencil in no.416(the retractable pencils)
2.) Lipstick was the @stilacosmetics liquid lipstick in the shade aria.

Lastly set my makeup with the @wetnwildbeauty @wetnwildindia coconut 3-in-1 face mist.. List of brushes :
@paccosmetic brushes 
1.)pencil brush no.202
2.)blending brush no.033
3.)small powder brush no.398
4.)blush brush which is used for the bronzer is no.302
5.)contour brush no.305
6.)spooley brush no.322
7.)used for smudging the liner no.385.
8.)beauty sponge .

@maccosmeticsindia brushes
1.) angular eyebrow brush no.208

Flat concealer brush was a non branded brush from amazon India .
